│ before folding (and includes FMF propagation). The bug is that the fsub(+0.0, │
│ X) path does not require no-NaNs, so it allows folding even when NaNs are     │
│ possible, changing NaN sign behavior and quieting behavior.                   │
│ Thus, the transformation is unsound without the nnan (no-NaNs) assumption.    │
│                                                                               │
